-- U.K. to Sell 8 Billion Pounds of 2040 Bonds at 1 Basis Point Above 2039s
-- Anchalee Worrachate
-- 2010-06-29T12:49:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/u-k-to-sell-8-billion-pounds-of-2040-bonds-at-1-basis-point-above-2039s.html

          
          
             The U.K. is selling 8 billion pounds
of 30-year notes that will be priced at 1 basis point more than
the outstanding 2039 gilt, according to two people with
knowledge of the deal.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
